name: #32 Princess
description: As she researched and read more about the Kingdom's tales, he began whispering vivid images into her dreams. This was how the Demon came to be, with the growing friction between the frantic and bright pictures that ran through her mind, lighting spark after spark until the light was too much to contain, and it shot down to the earth to become a full being that would, unknowingly, do its bidding, for the urge to guard knowledge that the Demon felt was the mere fiction of free will.\n\n[Paradox Gates II - The Eye God](https://eyeverse.world/paradox-gates)
